            <title><![CDATA[Stellar Blade sales top three million]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/stellar-blade-sales-top-three-million</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/stellar-blade-sales-top-three-million.1221501/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/stellar-blade-sales-top-three-million<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div role="main">
  
  <article>

    
<header>

  <div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>PC version sold one million copies in three days.</span>
      </p></div>

  

</header>  

<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Total sales for <em><a title="Games > Stellar Blade [30 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/stellar-blade">Stellar Blade</a></em> have surpassed three million units, developer <a title="Companies > SHIFT UP [30 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/shift-up">SHIFT UP</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/StellarBlade/status/1934563105302097943" target="_blank" rel="noopener">announced</a> (<a href="https://twitter.com/StellarBlade/status/1934653975451906359" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2</a>). <span id="more-974312"></span></p><p>The Korean <a title="Genres > Action [2,823 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,365 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> first launched for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,759 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> on April 26, 2024, followed by <a title="Platforms > PC [23,533 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3489700/Stellar_Blade/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/stellar-blade-fa21c3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a> on June 11, 2025. Sales surpassed <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/06/stellar-blade-sales-top-one-million">one million units</a> by June 25, 2024. According to <a href="https://bbs.ruliweb.com/news/read/211821" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ruliweb</a>, the PC version sold one million units in three days; and according to <a href="https://steamdb.info/app/3489700/charts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SteamDB</a>, it has an all-time peak of 192,078 concurrent players on Steam. That would also mean that the PlayStation 5 version sold around two million units by the time the PC version launched.</p></div>

        
    
  </article>
</div></div>]]></content:encoded>
