            <title><![CDATA[Cronos: The New Dawn physical edition announced for PS5]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/cronos-the-new-dawn-physical-edition-announced-for-ps5</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/cronos-the-new-dawn-physical-edition-announced-for-ps5.1221390/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/cronos-the-new-dawn-physical-edition-announced-for-ps5<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Distributed by Skybound Games.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Skybound Games [74 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/skybound-games">Skybound Games</a> will distribute a physical edition of third-person <a title="Genres > Survival [428 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/survival">survival</a> <a title="Genres > Horror [645 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/horror">horror game</a> <em><a title="Games > Cronos: The New Dawn [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/cronos-the-new-dawn">Cronos: The New Dawn</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,759 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> in the Americas, developer <a title="Companies > Bloober Team [99 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bloober-team">Bloober Team</a> <a href="https://ir.blooberteam.com/2025/06/17/cronos-the-new-dawn-trafi-do-sprzedazy-w-pudelkach-na-playstation-5-w-obu-amerykach-bloober-team-nawiazuje-wspolprace-ze-skybound-games-studios-inc/" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-974530"></span></p><p>“Skybound is a partner with exceptional competences in the field of global game distribution (it was responsible for the physical release of <em>The Calisto Protocol</em>, among others),” said Bloober Team CEO Piotr Babieno in a press release. “We are glad that we can develop this partnership with <em>Cronos: The New Dawn</em>. This is our strongest original title and we know that it will be another big step in the development of the Bloober Team Group. Boxed distribution is an important element of our distribution strategy and marketing mix.”</p><p><em>Cronos: The New Dawn</em> is due out for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2101960/Cronos_The_New_Dawn/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/cronos-the-new-dawn-85b409" target="_blank">Epic Games Store</a> this fall.</p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
